        <div class="glass rounded-lg p-4 text-sm">
          <table class="w-full text-sm">
            <tbody>
              <tr class="border-b border-white/5"><td class="py-1.5 font-mono text-white/60">network_id</td><td class="py-1.5 text-white/40">string, required — from POST /v1/networks</td></tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-white/5"><td class="py-1.5 font-mono text-white/60">timesteps</td><td class="py-1.5 text-white/40">int, required — number of simulation steps</td></tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-white/5"><td class="py-1.5 font-mono text-white/60">chip_model</td><td class="py-1.5 text-white/40">n1 | n2 (default n2) — processor target</td></tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-white/5"><td class="py-1.5 font-mono text-white/60">neuron_model</td><td class="py-1.5 text-white/40">cuba_lif | izhikevich | adex (default cuba_lif)</td></tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-white/5"><td class="py-1.5 font-mono text-white/60">stimuli</td><td class="py-1.5 text-white/40">array of population, neurons (optional), current</td></tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-white/5"><td class="py-1.5 font-mono text-white/60">learning</td><td class="py-1.5 text-white/40">enabled, graded, dendritic, noise, three_factor</td></tr>
              <tr><td class="py-1.5 font-mono text-white/60">rewards</td><td class="py-1.5 text-white/40">array of timestep, value — for 3-factor learning</td></tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="reveal mb-8">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
          <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-xs font-mono font-bold bg-blue-500/20 text-blue-400">GET</span>
          <code class="text-sm font-mono text-white/70">/v1/jobs/&#123;job_id&#125;</code>
          <span class="text-xs text-white/30">Auth required</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-white/40 mb-3">Get job status and summary results. Poll until status is "completed" or "failed".</p>
        <div class="glass rounded-lg p-4 text-sm">
          <p class="font-mono text-white/50 mb-2">Response fields (when completed):</p>
          <table class="w-full text-sm">
            <tbody>
              <tr class="border-b border-white/5"><td class="py-1.5 font-mono text-white/60">result.total_spikes</td><td class="py-1.5 text-white/40">int — total spikes across all neurons</td></tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-white/5"><td class="py-1.5 font-mono text-white/60">result.firing_rates</td><td class="py-1.5 text-white/40">per-population mean spikes per neuron per timestep</td></tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-white/5"><td class="py-1.5 font-mono text-white/60">result.spike_count_timeseries</td><td class="py-1.5 text-white/40">array — total spikes at each timestep</td></tr>
              <tr><td class="py-1.5 font-mono text-white/60">compute_seconds</td><td class="py-1.5 text-white/40">float — actual simulation compute time</td></tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="reveal mb-8">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
          <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-xs font-mono font-bold bg-green-500/20 text-green-400">POST</span>
          <code class="text-sm font-mono text-white/70">/v1/jobs/&#123;job_id&#125;/cancel</code>
          <span class="text-xs text-white/30">Auth required</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-white/40">Cancel a running or pending job. Credits refunded for unused compute.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="reveal mb-8">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
          <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-xs font-mono font-bold bg-blue-500/20 text-blue-400">GET</span>
          <code class="text-sm font-mono text-white/70">/v1/jobs/&#123;job_id&#125;/spikes</code>
          <span class="text-xs text-white/30">Auth required</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-white/40 mb-3">Full spike trains grouped by population with local neuron indices.</p>
        <div class="glass rounded-lg p-4 text-sm">
          <p class="font-mono text-white/50 mb-2">Response:</p>
          <pre class="text-xs font-mono text-white/50 mt-2"><code set:html={spikesResponse} /></pre>
        </div>
      </div>

